irheumatic drugs (DMARDs), or potent immunosuppressants (e.', 'Major', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/25009/', '[1] "Product Information. Olumiant (baricitinib)." Lilly, Eli and Company, Indianapolis, IN.[2] Cerner Multum, Inc. "UK Summary of Product Characteristics." O 0[3] Cerner Multum, Inc. "Australian Product Information." O 0', 'Apremilast, Pirfenidone, Belumosudil, Teprotumumab, Emapalumab, Baricitinib, Tofacitinib, Ravulizumab, Pegcetacoplan, Eculizumab, Sutimlimab', 'Anakinra, Apremilast, Pirfenidone, Belumosudil, Teprotumumab, Emapalumab, Ravulizumab, Pegcetacoplan, Eculizumab, Sutimlimab', 1767369485);
